/2024/10/16/24271680/anker-nano-car-charger-retractable-usb-c&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anker新款100W充电器几乎像 AirPods 一样小 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/6/24237701/anker-nano-charger-usb-c&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anker 回忆MagSafe iPhone 电池存在火灾风险 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/20/24249805/anker-recall-maggo-magsafe-iphone-battery-power-bank&quot;}]} &#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;ATzmFs&quot;>;需要明确的是，此特定版本不包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com 上提供的三个 AC 端口/Anker-Portable-Generator-Traveling-Emergcies/dp/B0D62GMQ3F?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;更昂贵的 Solix C300&lt;/a>;。也就是说，如果您不打算使用交流插头插入硬件，那么这是一个可行的替代方案。它提供相同的 90,000mAh (288Wh) 容量，并通过四个 USB-C 端口提供高达 300W 的功率（两个提供高达 140W 的功率，一个提供高达 140W 的功率...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/10/21/24275682/anker-solix-c300-dc-portable-power-station-iphone-16-pro-max-case-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/21/24275682/anker-solix-c300-dc-portable-power-station-iphone-16-pro-max-case-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/21/24275682/anker-solix-c300-dc-portable-power-station-iphone-16-pro-max-case-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-21T12:23:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-21T12:23:49-04:00</updated><title> GameCube 的复古风格在这款定制 PS5 DualSense 控制器中得以延续</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Killscreen CubeSense PS5 控制器，采用 GameCube 配色和操纵杆。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/p4Q3AHbYI4MV-OIQkakdPR0tI9I=/0x0:1178x785/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73667989/killscreen_cubesense1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Killscreen 的最新定制 DualSense 从 Nintendo GameCube 中汲取灵感。&lt;/em>; |图片：Killscreen&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&q